text: Shabnam Jahan is a Bangladeshi politician who is elected as Member of 11th Jatiya Sangsad of Reserved Seats for Women. She is a politician of Bangladesh Awami League. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Awami League politicians Category:11th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Bangladeshi women in politics Category:People from Dhaka District
